<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٧٢٣ - أَخْبَرَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5187">‌قُتَيْبَةُ </a>قَالَ: حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6785">‌أَبُو عَوَانَةَ </a>، عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5183">‌قَتَادَةَ </a>، عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/822">‌أَنَسٍ </a>قَالَ: قَالَ رَسُولُ اللهِ صَلَّى اللهُ عَلَيْهِ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٥١⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">وَسَلَّمَ:</span> <span class="c2">«الْبُصَاقُ فِي الْمَسْجِدِ خَطِيئَةٌ، وَكَفَّارَتُهَا دَفْنُهَا»</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>